            },
            {
                "comment": "He's a good teacher at what he teaches but his examples tend to be very simplified so you may get confused when doing real problems. Tests are basically if you have the equations you're find, if you miss one on your sheet you're probably in trouble.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 4
